INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(11,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower Pet Project','','','','','Organizational Support','Individuals','<p>If you are passionate about animals and have a love for helping pets find their forever homes, then join us as a Clean Kennels volunteer! Volunteers will work at our pet adoption center to help keep kennels clean and provide a comfortable living space for our furry friends.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks and Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Clean and sanitize kennels and surrounding areas to ensure a healthy living environment for the animals</li><li>Wash bedding, bowls, and toys to keep them clean and germ-free</li><li>Assist with daily feeding and watering of animals</li><li>Help with walking dogs and providing them with much-needed exercise</li><li>Provide socialization and companionship to animals awaiting their forever homes</li><li>Assist with other shelter duties as needed</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills and Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Must be 18 years of age or older</li><li>Passionate about animals and their welfare</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Ability to follow instructions and maintain cleanliness and orderliness</li><li>Ability to stand, walk, and bend for extended periods</li><li>Previous experience working with animals is preferred but not required</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Expectations:</strong></p><ul><li>Volunteers are expected to be punctual, dependable, and responsible.</li><li>Volunteers are expected to dress appropriately for the task and weather conditions.</li><li>Volunteers are expected to work collaboratively with shelter staff and other volunteers.</li><li>Volunteers are expected to treat all animals with kindness and respect.</li><li>Volunteers are expected to follow all shelter policies and procedures regarding the care of animals and their safety.</li></ul><p>This is an excel