INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(12,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower','','','','','Organizational Support','Individuals','<p>We are looking for enthusiastic volunteers to support our Fall Fundraising Gala. As an Event Silent Auction Support Volunteer, you will help us organize and execute a successful silent auction. You will work alongside other volunteers and staff members to ensure that the auction runs smoothly.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with setting up the silent auction area prior to the event</li><li>Help organize items for auction and ensure that they are properly displayed</li><li>Answer any questions guests may have about the items</li><li>Monitor the auction and take bids from guests</li><li>Notify winners of their items and distribute them after the auction has ended</li><li>Assist with cleaning up the auction area after the event</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong organizational skills and attention to detail</li><li>Excellent communication and customer service skills</li><li>Comfortable with basic math and money handling</li><li>Ability to work well in a team environment and follow instructions</li><li>Must be reliable and punctual</li></ul><p>Join us for an exciting evening and help us make a difference in our community!</p>','True','','False','San Francisco','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Nam vitae sodales dui, a tempus mi. Donec suscipit gravida placerat. Integer placerat erat non nibh gravida aliquet. Ut arcu mi, elementum in purus in, ullamcorper vulputate augue. Pellentesque egestas vestibulum maximus. Praesent ultricies ultricies semper. Sed vitae maximus nisi. Duis tincidunt tempus erat id tristique. Aliquam erat volutpat. Pellentesque imperdiet, arcu laoreet commodo ornare, mi ex