INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(13,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower','','','','','Cleanup','Individuals','<p>Volunteers will play an essential role in ensuring the success of our Fall Fundraising Gala. As an Event Cleanup Volunteer, you will be responsible for helping with the post-event cleanup. This includes taking out the trash, taking down tables and decorations, sweeping the floor, and ensuring that the venue is left clean and tidy after the event. Your participation will be crucial in helping us wrap up the event and prepare the venue for future events.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with the post-event cleanup of the venue</li><li>Remove all trash and debris from the event space</li><li>Take down tables, chairs, and decorations</li><li>Sweep and clean the floors</li><li>Assist with any other cleanup tasks as needed</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills Needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li><li>Physical stamina and the ability to stand, bend, and lift for extended periods</li><li>Attention to detail and the ability to follow instructions</li><li>Positive attitude and willingness to help out in any way possible</li><li>Prior experience with event cleanup is a plus, but not required</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Time Commitment:</strong></p><p>The Fall Fundraising Gala will take place on Saturday, October 15th, 2023, from 6:00 pm to 10:00 pm. We ask that Event Cleanup Volunteers arrive at the venue promptly at 10:00 pm and be available to help for a minimum of 2 hours.</p><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>Opportunity to be part of a fun and exciting fundraising event</li><li>Opportunity to meet and network with like-minded individuals</li><li>Opportunity to give back to the community and support a worthy cause</li><li>Letter of recommendation upon request</li></ul><p>We appreciate your interest in volunteering with us and l