INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(14,'False','Australia','Sunshine Beach','','','','','Cleanup','Groups;Individuals','<p>Join our volunteer team for a monthly beach cleanup at Sunshine Beach. As a volunteer, you&#39;ll be helping to keep our beautiful beach clean and safe for both people and wildlife. This is a great opportunity to make a positive impact on the community while enjoying the great outdoors.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks</strong>:</p><ul><li>Collect trash and debris along the beach</li><li>Sort and dispose of collected materials properly</li><li>Help with maintaining the beach&#39;s natural habitats</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills</strong>:</p><ul><li>Ability to work in a team and follow instructions</li><li>Comfortable working outdoors in various weather conditions</li><li>Physical ability to lift and carry objects</li><li>Attention to detail in sorting and disposing of materials</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Benefits</strong>:</p><ul><li>Opportunity to make a positive impact on the community</li><li>Meet new people and work with a great team of volunteers</li><li>Enjoy the outdoors and get some exercise</li><li>Gain experience in environmental conservation and stewardship</li></ul><p>Join us for our next monthly cleanup at Sunshine Beach and help us keep our beautiful beach clean and safe for all!</p>','True','','False','Sunshine Beach','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Nam vitae sodales dui, a tempus mi. Donec suscipit gravida placerat. Integer placerat erat non nibh gravida aliquet. Ut arcu mi, elementum in purus in, ullamcorper vulputate augue. Pellentesque egestas vestibulum maximus. Praesent ultricies ultricies semper. Sed vitae maximus nisi. Duis tincidunt tempus erat id tristique. Aliquam erat volutpat. Pellentes