INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(17,'False','United States','Macomb Park','','','','','Cleanup','Groups;Individuals','<p>Join us for a fun-filled day of community service and celebration at Macomb Park! We&#39;re looking for volunteers to help us with park cleanup and maintenance, followed by a potluck and BBQ for all volunteers and community members.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks</strong>:</p><ul><li>Pick up trash and debris within the park</li><li>Perform landscape maintenance (e.g. weeding, raking, planting)</li><li>Set up tables, chairs, and other equipment for the BBQ</li><li>Help with food preparation and serving during the potluck and BBQ</li><li>Assist with clean up after the event</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills and Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to work outdoors and perform physical tasks (e.g. lifting, bending, stooping)</li><li>Attention to detail and ability to follow instructions</li><li>Friendly and positive attitude, with excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Willingness to work collaboratively as part of a team</li><li>Food handling or preparation experience is a plus, but not required</li></ul><p style="text-align: justify;">This is a great opportunity to make a difference in your community while also having fun and meeting new people. We hope you&#39;ll join us for this exciting event!</p>','True','','False','San Francisco','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Quisque diam risus, fermentum facilisis eros eget, auctor lacinia dui</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Mauris nec rhoncus dui. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Donec eleifend varius lorem ut consectetur. Etiam non porta augue. Mauris condimentum sagittis ligula bibendum laoreet. </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong sty