INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(19,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower Ranch','','','50.0','','One-on-One Support','Individuals','<p>Volunteers will be an important part of our equine therapy program, providing support to our clients during after school sessions. Volunteers will work closely with clients and horses to ensure safety and a positive experience for everyone involved. Volunteers will assist with grooming, tacking, leading, and guiding horses during sessions.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li>Groom and tack horses before and after sessions</li><li>Guide and walk horses with clients during sessions</li><li>Assist clients with mounting and dismounting horses</li><li>Clean and maintain equipment and barn area</li><li>Assist instructors with setup and cleanup of sessions</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills Needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable working with horses and clients with disabilities</li><li>Basic horse handling skills and knowledge of horse behavior</li><li>Ability to follow directions and work as a team</li><li>Good communication skills and ability to interact positively with clients and staff</li><li>Ability to lift up to 50 pounds and perform physical tasks such as bending and walking</li></ul><p>Join us in making a difference in the lives of our clients and horses through equine therapy!</p>','True','','False','San Francisco','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Nam vitae sodales dui, a tempus mi. Donec suscipit gravida placerat. Integer placerat erat non nibh gravida aliquet. Ut arcu mi, elementum in purus in, ullamcorper vulputate augue. Pellentesque egestas vestibulum maximus. Praesent ultricies ultricies semper. Sed vitae maximus nisi. Duis tincidunt tempus erat id tristique. Aliquam erat volutpat. Pellentesque imperdiet, arcu laoree