INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(20,'False','United States','Swope Park meet @ Pavilion','','','','','Cleanup','Groups;Individuals','<p>As a volunteer for the Monthly Cleanup @ Swope Park, you will be joining our park cleanup program to help maintain and preserve the beauty of this local park. You will be participating in a variety of tasks including picking up trash and debris throughout the park, as well as performing landscaping maintenance to ensure a safe and clean environment for all visitors.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in the clean-up of the park, including trash and debris removal</li><li>Perform landscaping tasks such as weeding, pruning, and watering</li><li>Assist with the maintenance of trails and paths</li><li>Attend and participate in monthly clean-up events</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills and Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to perform physical tasks such as bending, lifting, and carrying up to 25 pounds</li><li>Ability to work outdoors in various weather conditions</li><li>Ability to work in a team environment</li><li>Strong communication skills</li><li>Willingness to follow instructions and take direction</li></ul><p>Volunteering for the Monthly Cleanup @ Swope Park is a great opportunity to give back to your community, meet new people, and contribute to the beautification of this important local park. We look forward to working with you!</p>','True','','False','Kansas City','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Nam vitae sodales dui, a tempus mi. Donec suscipit gravida placerat. Integer placerat erat non nibh gravida aliquet. Ut arcu mi, elementum in purus in, ullamcorper vulputate augue. Pellentesque egestas vestibulum maximus. Praesent ultricies ultricies semper. Sed vitae maximus nisi. Duis tincid