INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(21,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower Pet Project','','','','','Provide Transportation','Individuals','<p>We are seeking a responsible volunteer to help transport Gus, a lovable dog, to his annual checkup at the vet. The volunteer will drive Gus to the vet, wait during the appointment, and bring Gus back home safely. This is an important task, as Gus is a beloved member of our organization and we want to ensure he receives the proper care he needs.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks</strong>:</p><ul><li>Drive Gus to and from the vet for his annual checkup</li><li>Ensure Gus is safe and comfortable during transportation</li><li>Wait during the appointment and communicate with the vet if necessary</li><li>Follow any instructions provided by the vet</li><li>Provide any necessary feedback or information to Gus&#39; owners</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible and reliable</li><li>Safe and careful driver with a valid driver&#39;s license</li><li>Comfortable around dogs and able to handle a friendly, medium-sized dog</li><li>Good communication skills to relay information to Gus&#39; owners and the vet</li><li>Ability to follow instructions and attention to detail</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">We provide:</strong></p><ul><li>Information about Gus and his medical history</li><li>Clear instructions for transportation and communication with the vet</li><li>Reimbursement for gas expenses</li></ul><p>This is a great opportunity to help a beloved member of our organization and ensure he receives the proper care he needs. If you are responsible and comfortable around dogs, and want to make a difference, we encourage you to apply for this opportunity. Please email us at [contact email] if you are interested in becoming a volunteer for Transport Gus to Annual Checkup.</p>','True','','False','San Francisco','<p style="text-align: justify;"><s