INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(24,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower Ranch','','','','','Organizational Support','Individuals','<p>As a Recycling Center Support Team volunteer, you will be responsible for helping the public who bring their recycling to the center. You will guide them on where to put their glass, cardboard, and cans. This volunteer opportunity is perfect for anyone who wants to help reduce waste and promote recycling in the community.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks</strong>:</p><ul><li>Greet visitors and guide them on where to put their recycling.</li><li>Assist with organizing and separating the recycling materials.</li><li>Help maintain the cleanliness of the recycling center.</li><li>Educate the public on the importance of recycling.</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Excellent communication skills and ability to interact with the public.</li><li>Ability to work independently and in a team setting.</li><li>Knowledge of recycling and environmental conservation is a plus, but not required.</li><li>Ability to lift and move heavy items if needed.</li></ul><p>This volunteer position is an excellent way to make a difference in the community by promoting and facilitating recycling. Volunteers will gain experience working with the public, learning about recycling processes, and contributing to a cleaner environment.</p>','True','','False','San Francisco','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Nam vitae sodales dui, a tempus mi. Donec suscipit gravida placerat. Integer placerat erat non nibh gravida aliquet. Ut arcu mi, elementum in purus in, ullamcorper vulputate augue. Pellentesque egestas vestibulum maximus. Praesent ultricies ultricies semper. Sed vitae maximus nisi. Duis tincidunt tempus erat id tristique. Aliquam erat volutpat. Pelle