INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(25,'True','Canada','Salesforce Tower Pet Project','','','','','Foster/Adopt','Individuals','<p>Our animal shelter is looking for dedicated volunteers who are willing to provide a temporary home for dogs in need. As a Foster Volunteer, you will be responsible for welcoming a dog into your home, providing basic care, and helping prepare them for adoption. This is a rewarding opportunity to make a significant difference in the life of a dog while they wait for their forever home.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Type of Task:</strong></p><ul><li>Welcome a dog into your home and provide a safe and comfortable environment.</li><li>Provide basic care, including feeding, walking, and grooming.</li><li>Help socialize the dog and work on basic training, such as housebreaking.</li><li>Bring the dog to adoption events and provide updates to the shelter staff.</li><li>Communicate with shelter staff and veterinarians to ensure the dog&#39;s health and well-being.</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills Needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Must be at least 21 years old.</li><li>Must have a secure and stable living situation that is suitable for a dog.</li><li>Must be willing to provide basic care, including feeding, walking, and grooming.</li><li>Must have experience with dogs and be comfortable with basic training.</li><li>Must be able to provide transportation to adoption events and veterinary appointments.</li><li>Must have good communication skills and be able to work with shelter staff and veterinarians.</li></ul><p>This is a great opportunity for animal lovers who want to make a difference in the lives of dogs in need. Become a Foster Volunteer and help us provide a safe and loving temporary home for our shelter dogs!</p>','True','','False','Toronto','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-ali