INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(26,'False','United States','Salesforce Mountain Bike Park','','','','','Trail Building','Individuals','<p>We are looking for volunteers to assist in the maintenance of our bike park this spring season. As a volunteer, you will be helping repair trails, clean brush and debris, and prepare the park for the upcoming biking season.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li>Repairing trails and fixing any damage caused by winter weather</li><li>Clearing brush and debris from the park to make it safe for bikers</li><li>Checking the equipment and ensuring it is safe to use</li><li>Painting signs and touch up paint around the park</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills needed:</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to work outdoors and in varying weather conditions</li><li>Good communication and team-working skills</li><li>Ability to perform light physical work</li><li>Basic knowledge of trail maintenance and bike park care is a plus but not required</li></ul><p style="text-align: justify;">We welcome volunteers of all ages and abilities. This is a great opportunity for outdoor enthusiasts who want to give back to their community while enjoying the beautiful spring weather. Join us in our efforts to provide a safe and fun environment for bikers of all ages and skill levels.</p>','True','','False','Chicago','','111 W Illinois St','60654','IL','False','','America/Chicago','Spring Maintenance @ Bike Park','/file-asset-public/FlowToolKit_VolunteerTrailBuilding1','','5');
INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(27,'False','Canada','Salesforce Tower','','','','','Organizational Support','Individuals','<p>Our Fall Fundraising Gala is a major event for our organization and we need volunteers to help set up the event. As an Event Setup Volunteer, you will be an essential part of the team that transforms the venue into a festive and welcoming space for our guests.</p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with the setup of tables, chairs, and decorations</li><li>Help with the placement of food and beverage stations</li><li>Assist with the setup of any audiovisual equipment</li><li>Work with other volunteers and staff to ensure everything is ready for the event</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Skills</strong>:</p><ul><li>Ability to follow instructions and work as part of a team</li><li>Physically capable of lifting and moving items</li><li>Attention to detail and ability to work efficiently</li><li>Flexibility and willingness to adapt to changing circumstances</li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">What to Expect:</strong></p><ul><li>A fun and rewarding experience working with a team of dedicated volunteers and staff</li><li>The opportunity to contribute to the success of a major fundraising event</li><li>The chance to learn new skills and gain experience in event planning and setup</li></ul><p>Join us as an Event Setup Volunteer and help us create an amazing experience for our guests at our Fall Fundraising Gala!</p>','True','','False','San Francisco','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 14px;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Nam vitae sodales dui, a tempus mi. Donec suscipit gravida placerat. Integer placerat erat non nibh gravida aliquet. Ut arcu mi, elementum in purus in, ullamcorper vulputate augue. Pellentesque egestas vestibulum maximus. Praesent ultricies ultricies semp