INSERT INTO "GW_Volunteers__Volunteer_Job__c" VALUES(28,'True','United States','Salesforce Food Bank','','','','','Food Sorting','Groups;Individuals;Youth/Children','<p><strong style="font-size: 22px;">Evening Food Sorting @ Food Bank</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Overview</strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">:</span></p><ul><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Help fight hunger in your community by volunteering at the local food bank</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Sort and package donated food for distribution to families in need</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">No prior experience necessary; training provided on-site</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Great opportunity to give back as an individual or as a team</span></li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Tasks and Roles:</strong></p><ul><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Sort donated food by category</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Check for expiration dates and quality of donated food</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Package food in boxes for distribution</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Help maintain the cleanliness of the sorting area</span></li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Expectations</strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">:</span></p><ul><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Volunteers should dress comfortably and be prepared to stand for extended periods of time</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Brief orientation and training provided upon check-in</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Volunteers can expect to work alongside other dedicated volunteers</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">A great opportunity to give back to the community while building relationships with like-minded individuals</span></li></ul><p><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Impact:</strong></p><ul><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">By volunteering, you will help ensure that families in need have access to nutritious food</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Make a tangible difference in the lives of those struggling with food insecurity</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Join the fight against hunger and be a part of the solution in your community.</span></li></ul><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">If you&#39;re interested in volunteering for this position, you can expect to work in a fast-paced and dynamic environment. Volunteers play an integral role in the food bank&#39;s efforts to alleviate hunger in the community. You&#39;ll be working alongside other passionate volunteers who share your commitment to making a difference. No prior experience is necessary, and you&#39;ll receive a brief orientation and training upon check-in. So why wait? Sign up today and help us fight hunger in your community!</span></p>','True','','False','Burlington','<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Quisque diam risus, fermentum facilisis eros eget, auctor lacinia dui</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Mauris nec rhoncus dui. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Interdum et malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Donec eleifend varius lorem ut consectetur. Etiam non porta augue. Mauris condimentum sagittis ligula bibendum laoreet. </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;">Cras dapibus elit at lacus euismod viverra ac porttitor felis</strong>. </p><p style="text-align: justify;">Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Etiam semper dui quis tellus hendrerit mollis. Orci varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Praesent tellus nulla, rhoncus ac vulputate a, varius ac sem. Quisque suscipit eleifend viverra. Proin sed lorem eget sapien volutpat accumsan quis quis metus. Etiam leo arcu, molestie